{"tid":878142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【美人計3之呃飯食】神隱兩星期再出動 Karen一晚約7男撐枱腳","createTime":"2018-10-27T01:43:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T13:32:25.000Z","uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"10ecb441116888a28e6bd5d944701a6e788cbf69","tid":878142,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:43:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181026&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58839658\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181026%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58839658&d=9iVdLhF2oXh1GoYoeFC2uo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=87976a32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181026%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58839658&h=a002056e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181026&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58839658</a><br />\n<br />\n【美人計3之呃飯食】神隱兩星期再出動 Karen一晚約7男撐枱腳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/094219_631f77c5121d1bca040b6aaf320a0e1c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F094219_631f77c5121d1bca040b6aaf320a0e1c.png&h=cfb4b619&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/094251_94fcd4eb7ea0751f577ea787a7b3eecc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F094251_94fcd4eb7ea0751f577ea787a7b3eecc.png&h=21496239&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有少女以「美人飯局」手法，在交友App相約男網友出來帶到指定地點晚飯，埋單劏到網友一頸血，結果有不少「巴打」感到受騙。記者當場踢爆自稱Karen的少女所作所為後，僅翌日見她曾返回涉事的太子唐三樓Cafe，但她沒有再運作「美人飯局」，之後數天，記者亦未見Karen再出現在該Cafe。<br />\n<br />\n以為「美人」良心發現？記者昨日再於Cafe留下守候，發現神隱兩星期的Karen再次出動，這次她明顯經過悉心打扮，穿白色上衣衫及一條藍色超短裙褲，晚上近6時，開始帶「飯腳男」上Cafe撐枱腳，同樣相約在太子始創中心附近等候，再扮搵路，最後上餐廳。<br />\n<br />\n記者目測，由晚上6時至10時半，先後有7名男子被她帶上cafe，但做法與早前有些不同，Karen沒有再帶外賣盒離開，而是與每位「飯腳男」都食足一餐飯，只是食飯時間較快，一般在半小時內完成，然後她會與對方一齊走，在樓下才分道揚鑣，Karen就急急腳去會合下一個「飯腳男」。"},{"pid":"986822fc970c75aa15bd106ed61c5e63fbb2f762","tid":878142,"uid":130105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:44:53.000Z","msg":"個樣咁恐佈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd490ff50040c33e8e7e8130c36f193ea74ae4d","tid":878142,"uid":60092,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:45:49.000Z","msg":"呢啲男人真係好羞家，咁豬都唔彈鐘仲俾佢呃到幾轉錢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b705b1e1d1636da19633a900100d4c68010c751","tid":878142,"uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:46:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/094655_4e2477b4bcc2fc573c3f1510377a7c86.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F094655_4e2477b4bcc2fc573c3f1510377a7c86.png&h=0a70d6d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54b32eadae0baecf748735dd7e3cee4bee70d156","tid":878142,"uid":123014,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:48:57.000Z","msg":"唔知有幾多巴打受害呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n靚既比佢呃飯食 都冇咁肉痛<br />\n呢個見到 就走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7f790a4b514a56012dc614c6288a066d834772","tid":878142,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:49:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">這次她明顯經過悉心打扮，穿白色上衣衫及一條藍色超短裙褲</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次有誠意少少，雖然都係豬🐷"},{"pid":"d471dc5e4b53d1ee9af6500cc7a3a875845ecf3d","tid":878142,"uid":132587,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:51:17.000Z","msg":"究竟港男係餓到一個咩既程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /